avdta.network.node.policy

Class TransitFirst

  • java.lang.Object
    • avdta.network.node.policy.IntersectionPolicy
      • avdta.network.node.policy.TransitFirst
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<Vehicle>

    public class TransitFirst
extends IntersectionPolicy
    This policy extends another IntersectionPolicy and operates as follows: If the Vehicle is transit, it has priority; otherwise, the default IntersectionPolicy is used.
